#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn17:2.12.32"
msgid "8. Brahmalokūpagama"
msgstr ""

#. </h2><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.13"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.196"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc53"></a>
msgctxt "dn17:2.13.1"
msgid "Atha kho, ānanda, rājā mahāsudassano na cirasseva kālamakāsi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn17:2.13.2"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, ānanda, gahapatissa vā gahapatiputtassa vā manuññaṃ bhojanaṃ "
"bhuttāvissa bhattasammado hoti; evameva kho, ānanda, rañño mahāsudassanassa "
"māraṇantikā vedanā ahosi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn17:2.13.3"
msgid "Kālaṅkato ca, ānanda, rājā mahāsudassano sugatiṃ brahmalokaṃ upapajji."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: kumārakīḷaṃ → … kīḷitaṃ (bj, mr) | … kīḷikaṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "dn17:2.13.4"
msgid "Rājā, ānanda, mahāsudassano caturāsīti vassasahassāni kumārakīḷaṃ kīḷi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn17:2.13.5"
msgid "Caturāsīti vassasahassāni oparajjaṃ kāresi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn17:2.13.6"
msgid "Caturāsīti vassasahassāni rajjaṃ kāresi."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: brahmacariyaṃ cari → brahmacariyaṃ ācari (s1-3, km) | brahma­cari­ya­macari (mr)
#. VAR: gihibhūto → gihībhūto (bj, pts1) | gīhibhūto (km)
msgctxt "dn17:2.13.7"
msgid "Caturāsīti vassasahassāni gihibhūto dhamme pāsāde brahmacariyaṃ cari."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn17:2.13.8"
msgid ""
"So cattāro brahmavihāre bhāvetvā kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā brahmalokūpago "
"ahosi."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.14"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.197"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc54"></a>
msgctxt "dn17:2.14.1"
msgid "Siyā kho panānanda, evamassa:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn17:2.14.2"
msgid "‘añño nūna tena samayena rājā mahāsudassano ahosī’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn17:2.14.3"
msgid ""
"na kho panetaṃ, ānanda, evaṃ daṭṭhabbaṃ. Ahaṃ tena samayena rājā "
"mahāsudassano ahosiṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn17:2.14.4"
msgid ""
"Mama tāni caturāsīti nagarasahassāni kusāvatīrājadhānippamukhāni, mama tāni "
"caturāsīti pāsādasahassāni dhammapāsādappamukhāni, mama tāni caturāsīti "
"kūṭāgārasahassāni mahāviyūhakūṭāgārappamukhāni, mama tāni caturāsīti "
"pallaṅkasahassāni sovaṇṇamayāni rūpiyamayāni dantamayāni sāramayāni "
"gonakatthatāni paṭikatthatāni paṭalikatthatāni "
"kadalimigapavarapaccattharaṇāni sauttaracchadāni ubhatolohitakūpadhānāni, "
"mama tāni caturāsīti nāgasahassāni sovaṇṇālaṅkārāni sovaṇṇadhajāni "
"hemajālapaṭicchannāni uposathanāgarājappamukhāni, mama tāni caturāsīti "
"assasahassāni sovaṇṇālaṅkārāni sovaṇṇadhajāni hemajālapaṭicchannāni "
"valāhakaassarājappamukhāni, mama tāni caturāsīti rathasahassāni "
"sīhacammaparivārāni byagghacammaparivārāni dīpicammaparivārāni "
"paṇḍukambalaparivārāni sovaṇṇālaṅkārāni sovaṇṇadhajāni hemajālapaṭicchannāni "
"vejayantarathappamukhāni, mama tāni caturāsīti maṇisahassāni "
"maṇiratanappamukhāni, mama tāni caturāsīti itthisahassāni "
"subhaddādevippamukhāni, mama tāni caturāsīti gahapatisahassāni "
"gahapatiratanappamukhāni, mama tāni caturāsīti khattiyasahassāni anuyantāni "
"pariṇāyakaratanappamukhāni, mama tāni caturāsīti dhenusahassāni "
"duhasandanāni kaṃsūpadhāraṇāni, mama tāni caturāsīti vatthakoṭisahassāni "
"khomasukhumānaṃ kappāsikasukhumānaṃ koseyyasukhumānaṃ kambalasukhumānaṃ, "
"mama tāni caturāsīti thālipākasahassāni sāyaṃ pātaṃ bhattābhihāro "
"abhihariyittha."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.15"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.198"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc55"></a>
msgctxt "dn17:2.15.1"
msgid ""
"Tesaṃ kho panānanda, caturāsītinagarasahassānaṃ ekaññeva taṃ nagaraṃ hoti, "
"yaṃ tena samayena ajjhāvasāmi yadidaṃ kusāvatī rājadhānī."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn17:2.15.2"
msgid ""
"Tesaṃ kho panānanda, caturāsīti pāsādasahassānaṃ ekoyeva so pāsādo hoti, yaṃ "
"tena samayena ajjhāvasāmi yadidaṃ dhammo pāsādo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn17:2.15.3"
msgid ""
"Tesaṃ kho panānanda, caturāsīti kūṭāgārasahassānaṃ ekaññeva taṃ kūṭāgāraṃ "
"hoti, yaṃ tena samayena ajjhāvasāmi yadidaṃ mahāviyūhaṃ kūṭāgāraṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn17:2.15.4"
msgid ""
"Tesaṃ kho panānanda, caturāsīti pallaṅkasahassānaṃ ekoyeva so pallaṅko hoti, "
"yaṃ tena samayena paribhuñjāmi yadidaṃ sovaṇṇamayo vā rūpiyamayo vā "
"dantamayo vā sāramayo vā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn17:2.15.5"
msgid ""
"Tesaṃ kho panānanda, caturāsīti nāgasahassānaṃ ekoyeva so nāgo hoti, yaṃ "
"tena samayena abhiruhāmi yadidaṃ uposatho nāgarājā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn17:2.15.6"
msgid ""
"Tesaṃ kho panānanda, caturāsīti assasahassānaṃ ekoyeva so asso hoti, yaṃ "
"tena samayena abhiruhāmi yadidaṃ valāhako assarājā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn17:2.15.7"
msgid ""
"Tesaṃ kho panānanda, caturāsīti rathasahassānaṃ ekoyeva so ratho hoti, yaṃ "
"tena samayena abhiruhāmi yadidaṃ vejayantaratho."
msgstr ""

# https://discourse.suttacentral.net/t/is-there-such-a-word-as-velamika/2952
msgctxt "dn17:2.15.8"
msgid ""
"Tesaṃ kho panānanda, caturāsīti itthisahassānaṃ ekāyeva sā itthī hoti, yā "
"tena samayena paccupaṭṭhāti khattiyānī vā vessinī vā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn17:2.15.9"
msgid ""
"Tesaṃ kho panānanda, caturāsīti vatthakoṭisahassānaṃ ekaṃyeva taṃ dussayugaṃ "
"hoti, yaṃ tena samayena paridahāmi khomasukhumaṃ vā kappāsikasukhumaṃ vā "
"koseyyasukhumaṃ vā kambalasukhumaṃ vā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn17:2.15.10"
msgid ""
"Tesaṃ kho panānanda, caturāsīti thālipākasahassānaṃ ekoyeva so thālipāko "
"hoti, yato nāḷikodanaparamaṃ bhuñjāmi tadupiyañca sūpeyyaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.16"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc56"></a>
msgctxt "dn17:2.16.1"
msgid "Passānanda, sabbete saṅkhārā atītā niruddhā vipariṇatā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn17:2.16.2"
msgid "Evaṃ aniccā kho, ānanda, saṅkhārā;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn17:2.16.3"
msgid "evaṃ addhuvā kho, ānanda, saṅkhārā;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn17:2.16.4"
msgid "evaṃ anassāsikā kho, ānanda, saṅkhārā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn17:2.16.5"
msgid ""
"Yāvañcidaṃ, ānanda, alameva sabbasaṅkhāresu nibbindituṃ, alaṃ virajjituṃ, "
"alaṃ vimuccituṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2.17"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.199"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc57"></a>
msgctxt "dn17:2.17.1"
msgid ""
"Chakkhattuṃ kho panāhaṃ, ānanda, abhijānāmi imasmiṃ padese sarīraṃ "
"nikkhipitaṃ, tañca kho rājāva samāno cakkavattī dhammiko dhammarājā "
"cāturanto vijitāvī janapadatthāvariyappatto sattaratanasamannāgato, ayaṃ "
"sattamo sarīranikkhepo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn17:2.17.2"
msgid ""
"Na kho panāhaṃ, ānanda, taṃ padesaṃ samanupassāmi sadevake loke samārake "
"sabrahmake sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiyā pajāya sadevamanussāya yattha tathāgato "
"aṭṭhamaṃ sarīraṃ nikkhipeyyā”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc58"></a>
msgctxt "dn17:2.17.3"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn17:2.17.4"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvāna sugato athāparaṃ etadavoca satthā:"
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc59"></a>
msgctxt "dn17:2.17.5"
msgid "“Aniccā vata saṅkhārā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn17:2.17.6"
msgid "uppādavayadhammino;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn17:2.17.7"
msgid "Uppajjitvā nirujjhanti,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn17:2.17.8"
msgid "tesaṃ vūpasamo sukho”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "dn17:2.17.9"
msgid "Mahāsudassanasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
